 Select the VPC on your services page
 Click on launch VPC wizard
  Click on create VPC. 
 Enter the VPC name as private VPC, IPV4 CIDR block as 10.0.0.0/24
 In IPV4 CIDR block choose amazon provided IPV6 CIDR block
. Click on create VPC
 Then VPC will be successfully created
Open the subnet option
9. Then click on create a subnet.
10. Select the created VPC.
11.   Name the subnet as per your convenience,
10 Check in the IPV6 only
11. In the IPV6 CIDR block in the second line there is space to enter a number, enter 04
12. Then click on add subnet to create add more subnets, here in the IPV6 block enter the number 06
13. Then click create a subnet.
14. Go to the internet gateway, click on create internet gateway.
15. Enter the name, then click on create internet gateway.
16. Right-click on the created internet gateway, click on attach to VPC
17. Select the VPC that you have created.
18. Then click on attach internet gateway

(Show the internet gateway page as output to mam)
